{"tid":455052,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我既努力原來係多餘","createTime":"2017-11-01T17:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T18:59:12.000Z","uid":147571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"60592e404743f5e104ce26c2b9c91b2236658d1a","tid":455052,"uid":147571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T17:41:34.000Z","msg":"呢幾日都好唔開心 一到夜晚更加一發不可收拾 崩潰到要喊先得 <br />\n以為大家變左 但我唔變就可以 但原來得我唔變係無用<br />\n我以為我既努力 可以keep住我地既友情 <br />\n我以為我既主動 可以令你feel到我對你既重視<br />\n<br />\n成日話重視我呢個朋友 但點解我feel唔到 <br />\n點解我做咁多野 你都feel唔到<br />\n係我要求高定點 <br />\n<br />\n自問好努力去維繫每一段友情 但原來好多野唔係我努力就得<br />\n點解次次我交個心出黎比人都係咁 <br />\n係我太敏感定你覺得太小事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我真係好撚hurt呀屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"641a74e031e41b8bacef25a973c5124abc9ac7d2","tid":455052,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T17:50:44.000Z","msg":"算啦 多一個唔多"},{"pid":"ab237d24166ca3655a1332d2ded90aaad33ddf4a","tid":455052,"uid":147571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T17:51:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>算啦 多一個唔多</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n原來一切都係我以為 我真係好on9"},{"pid":"6a941381f262e3af087c813d5265050b1128e35d","tid":455052,"uid":87439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T17:52:24.000Z","msg":"有時大家唔同步，點努力都無用"},{"pid":"bf1726dfbb69a802e58a770e028a9ebb81f653bc","tid":455052,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T17:55:24.000Z","msg":"一般人都傾同比自己弱既人相處<br />\n樓主系米太有主見or強勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6aef61c6b578404149040d3933d3e6fff31fe5db","tid":455052,"uid":147571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T18:00:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時大家唔同步，點努力都無用</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我以為大家已經有左共識 但原來唔係 <br />\n以為大家感情已經夠堅固 <br />\n但原來唔係 所有野都係我一廂情願<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3597acd1cee38b223416ca3e88bcfce7ba8b2793","tid":455052,"uid":147571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T18:01:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>一般人都傾同比自己弱既人相處<br />\n樓主系米太有主見or強勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n算係 佢地會睇我頭"},{"pid":"6f0bea29e814634bb5f6ba71090f3383f87aa254","tid":455052,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T18:01:26.000Z","msg":"你講下咩事先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d9f316475f2b35de196fc66f09056ce8793bbe6","tid":455052,"uid":147571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T18:05:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你講下咩事先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好多野積積埋埋 搞到我好灰 <br />\n-好早約左佢 但佢要同人補習 推到好夜 都算 但早一日我問佢先講 <br />\n-同兩個識左差唔多10年既朋友無再聯絡<br />\n-以為同個fd相處方式係岩大家 但原來係唔岩"},{"pid":"76d572a892d42ebce250d4e2810f6c732feb7eff","tid":455052,"uid":58778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T18:59:12.000Z","msg":"維繫一段感情係咪真係要咁辛苦？<br />\n有時越努力越吃力 最後只會苦了自己"}]}